trans-unit.source: I strongly believe...<\r><\n>Albert's research must stop.

seg-source.mrk: I strongly believe...<\r><\n>Albert's research must stop.

target.mrk: Acredito firmemente...<\r><\n> A pesquisa de Albert deve parar.

trans-unit.source: We can't build the future on your<\r><\n>empty optimism!

seg-source.mrk: We can't build the future on your<\r><\n>empty optimism!

target.mrk: No podemos construir o futuro com o seu<\r><\n> otimismo vazio!

trans-unit.source: Say what you will, I cannot agree to this.

seg-source.mrk: Say what you will, I cannot agree to this.

target.mrk: Diga o que quiser, no posso concordar com isso.

trans-unit.source: At every turn, you've ignorantly<\r><\n>blocked my research...

seg-source.mrk: At every turn, you've ignorantly<\r><\n>blocked my research...

trans-unit.source: I see the committee is in agreement.

seg-source.mrk: I see the committee is in agreement.

target.mrk: Vejo que o comit est de acordo.

trans-unit.source: And so... the department chooses Thomas Light's<\r><\n>research into robots with independent thought.

seg-source.mrk: And so... the department chooses Thomas Light's<\r><\n>research into robots with independent thought.

target.mrk: E assim... o departamento escolhe a pesquisa de Thomas Light <\r><\n> sobre robs com pensamento independente.

trans-unit.source: Why...?<\r><\n>Why are you fools so blind!?
Ungh...<\r><\n>Bad memories make the worst dreams...

seg-source.mrk: Ungh...<\r><\n>Bad memories make the worst dreams...

target.mrk: Ungh...<\r><\n> Memrias ruins criam os piores sonhos...

trans-unit.source: A genius of my caliber needs sleep to <\r><\n>keep his brain in gear.

seg-source.mrk: A genius of my caliber needs sleep to <\r><\n>keep his brain in gear.

target.mrk: Um gnio do meu calibre precisa dormir para <\r><\n>manter seu crebro funcionando.
Sim...<\r><\n>Agora eu vou te mostrar, Light!

trans-unit.source: One day the world will know... I was right all along!

seg-source.mrk: One day the world will know...

target.mrk: Eu estava certo o tempo todo!
